#

Grilled Chimichurri Flank Steak

25 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

ArgentinianAmerican

Course:

Main DishDinner

Tags:

GrilledSteakChimichurriEasy

Description

Juicy flank steak marinated in a vibrant chimichurri sauce, grilled to perfection for a burst of flavor in every bite.

Ingredients

  • flank steak: 1.5 pounds
  • fresh parsley: 1 cup, chopped
  • garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • red wine vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 1/2 cup
  • oregano: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • red pepper flakes: 1/2 teaspoon (optional)
